              "type": "stat_block_section",
              "unit": "feet"
            },
            "subtype": "ability",
            "text": "The court historian monotonously recites facts to distract a creature within 30 feet that can hear them. The target is off-guard for 1 round.",
            "traits": [
              {
                "alternate_link": {
